N2  - This paper presents a method for computing the lot size to be produced each time each product is scheduled for production when all products are produced on a single machine. The method also computes the distribution of lot size for each product. The demand for each product is a stochastic variable with known distribution, distributed independently for nonoverlapping time periods and identically for equal time periods.
